summary: Now accepting Twitch clips and Youtube videos!
title: Now accepting Twitch clips and Youtube videos!
body:
As this blog goes reaches the 5 years on Tumblr, we decided to start accepting submissions of Twitch clips and Youtube videos in addition to quotes! Now submissions are not limited to funny one-liners, but include any hilarious gaming moments that you’ve come across. As always, make sure to send a working link to the video or clip that you want to submit. If the video is over 10 minutes, also include a time stamp to the moment that you want to submit.

Again, thank you for all the support, and happy gaming!

question: Got any favorite youtubers?
answer:
I used to really like Jacksepticeye, I enjoyed watching his gameplays. He has a fun and over all positive energy. I think we need more generally supportive people in our media.

I also liked Marzia’s videos before she closed her account. Even after I stopped liking Pewdiepie’s videos, I thought Marzia’s was cute. Just fun little activities that she did.

JennaMarbles is pretty funny too :)
